title: Secret talks end with Beijing brokered Saudi Arabia and Iran deal which will leave US wary
description: Saudi Arabia and Iran have announced they will resume ties after years of hostility.

title: Police had been warned about Hamburg shooter's mental health, officials say
description: The gunman who killed seven people at a Jehovah's Witness building in Hamburg was a former member of the congregation who police had been warned about, German police have said.

title: Unborn baby among those killed in shooting at Jehovah's Witness building in Hamburg
description: The unborn baby of a woman who was seven months pregnant was among those killed during a mass shooting at a Jehovah's Witness building in the German city of Hamburg.

title: Girl abducted from shopping centre in 2018 found in Mexico
description: A girl from the United States who went missing in October 2018 has been found alive and well in Mexico, the FBI has said.
